<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Educación & Tecnología — El Futuro del Aprendizaje</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --ink: #0a0e1a;
    --paper: #f5f0e8;
    --electric: #00e5ff;
    --amber: #ffb300;
    --coral: #ff4d6d;
    --mint: #00c896;
    --grid: rgba(0,229,255,0.07);
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    cursor: none;
  }

  /* Custom cursor */
  .cursor {
    position: fixed;
    width: 12px; height: 12px;
    background: var(--electric);
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9999;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    transition: transform 0.1s, width 0.3s, height 0.3s, opacity 0.3s;
    mix-blend-mode: screen;
  }
  .cursor-ring {
    position: fixed;
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--electric);
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9998;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    transition: transform 0.15s ease-out, width 0.3s, height 0.3s;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  /* Grid background */
  .grid-bg {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(var(--grid) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, var(--grid) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  /* Floating particles */
  .particles { position: fixed; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0; }
  .particle {
    position: absolute;
    width: 2px; height: 2px;
    background: var(--electric);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: float linear infinite;
    opacity: 0;
  }
  @keyframes float {
    0% { transform: translateY(100vh) translateX(0); opacity: 0; }
    10% { opacity: 0.8; }
    90% { opacity: 0.4; }
    100% { transform: translateY(-10vh) translateX(40px); opacity: 0; }
  }

  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 80px 8vw;
    z-index: 2;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-label {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--electric);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.2s forwards;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .hero-label::before {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 40px; height: 1px;
    background: var(--electric);
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 9vw, 9rem);
    line-height: 0.92;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease 0.4s forwards;
  }
  .hero-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--electric);
    display: block;
  }
  .hero-title span {
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px var(--paper);
    color: transparent;
    display: block;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: clamp(0.75rem, 1.4vw, 1rem);
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.5);
    max-width: 420px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease 0.6s forwards;
  }

  .hero-scroll {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.4);
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease 0.8s forwards;
  }
  .scroll-line {
    width: 60px; height: 1px;
    background: rgba(245,240,232,0.3);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .scroll-line::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: var(--electric);
    animation: scanLine 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    transform: translateX(-100%);
  }
  @keyframes scanLine {
    0% { transform: translateX(-100%); }
    100% { transform: translateX(100%); }
  }

  /* Big circuit decoration */
  .circuit-art {
    position: absolute;
    right: -5%;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: clamp(300px, 45vw, 700px);
    opacity: 0.12;
    animation: fadeIn 2s ease 1s forwards;
    opacity: 0;
  }
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    to { opacity: 0.12; }
  }

  /* Sections */
  section {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    padding: 120px 8vw;
  }

  /* Section tag */
  .s-tag {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.35em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--electric);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }
  .s-tag::after {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 80px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--electric);
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  /* Card grid */
  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(min(100%, 320px), 1fr));
    gap: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .card {
    background: rgba(245,240,232,0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,240,232,0.06);
    padding: 48px 40px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: background 0.4s, border-color 0.4s, transform 0.4s;
    cursor: none;
  }
  .card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent, var(--electric)) 0%, transparent 60%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.4s;
  }
  .card:hover {
    background: rgba(245,240,232,0.06);
    border-color: rgba(245,240,232,0.15);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }
  .card:hover::before { opacity: 0.05; }

  .card-num {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--accent, var(--electric));
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    display: block;
  }
  .card-icon {
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    display: block;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 12px var(--accent, var(--electric)));
    transition: filter 0.3s;
  }
  .card:hover .card-icon {
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 24px var(--accent, var(--electric)));
  }
  .card h3 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .card p {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.55);
  }

  /* Big text block */
  .big-block {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 100px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .big-block { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 60px; }
    .circuit-art { display: none; }
  }

  .big-num {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(6rem, 15vw, 16rem);
    line-height: 1;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(245,240,232,0.1);
    color: transparent;
    user-select: none;
    position: relative;
    left: -4px;
  }

  .body-text {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.9);
  }
  .body-text .highlight {
    color: var(--electric);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .body-text .amber { color: var(--amber); font-style: italic; }
  .body-text .coral { color: var(--coral); font-style: italic; }
  .body-text .mint { color: var(--mint); font-style: italic; }

  /* Challenges */
  .challenges-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .challenges-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  .challenge-item {
    padding: 40px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,240,232,0.07);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.4s;
  }
  .challenge-item::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--c, var(--coral));
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transform-origin: left;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease;
  }
  .challenge-item:hover::after { transform: scaleX(1); }
  .challenge-item:hover { background: rgba(245,240,232,0.03); }
  .challenge-item .ci-label {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--c, var(--coral));
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .challenge-item h4 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .challenge-item p {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.45);
  }

  /* Quote */
  .quote-section {
    background: rgba(0,229,255,0.04);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.12);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.12);
  }
  .big-quote {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4.5vw, 4rem);
    line-height: 1.25;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
  }
  .big-quote::before {
    content: '"';
    font-size: 12rem;
    line-height: 0.7;
    color: var(--electric);
    opacity: 0.1;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: -20px;
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
  }

  /* Footer */
  footer {
    z-index: 2;
    position: relative;
    padding: 60px 8vw 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(245,240,232,0.06);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .footer-brand {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .footer-note {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.3);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .footer-dot {
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--electric);
    display: inline-block;
    margin: 0 8px;
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 0.3; transform: scale(0.6); }
  }

  /* Animations */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(40px);
    transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
  }
  .reveal.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  /* Horizontal rule */
  .hr-fancy {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(245,240,232,0.07);
    margin: 0 8vw;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  /* Noise overlay */
  body::after {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 512 512' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='1'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    opacity: 0.028;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1000;
  }

  /* Scanline */
  .scanline {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--electric), transparent);
    animation: scan 8s linear infinite;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 998;
    opacity: 0.25;
  }
  @keyframes scan {
    0% { top: -3px; }
    100% { top: 100vh; }
  }

  /* Stats bar */
  .stats-bar {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,240,232,0.07);
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-top: 80px;
  }
  .stat {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 40px 32px;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(245,240,232,0.07);
    transition: background 0.4s;
  }
  .stat:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .stat:hover { background: rgba(245,240,232,0.04); }
  .stat-val {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--sv-c, var(--electric));
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .stat-lbl {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(245,240,232,0.35);
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .stats-bar { flex-direction: column; }
    .stat { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245,240,232,0.07); }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Custom Cursor -->
<div class="cursor" id="cursor"></div>
<div class="cursor-ring" id="cursor-ring"></div>

<!-- Scanline -->
<div class="scanline"></div>

<!-- Grid Background -->
<div class="grid-bg"></div>

<!-- Particles -->
<div class="particles" id="particles"></div>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">

  <!-- Circuit SVG decoration -->
  <svg class="circuit-art" viewBox="0 0 500 500" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
    <circle cx="250" cy="250" r="200" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5"/>
    <circle cx="250" cy="250" r="150" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="8 4"/>
    <circle cx="250" cy="250" r="90" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5"/>
    <circle cx="250" cy="250" r="30" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"/>
    <circle cx="250" cy="250" r="8" fill="currentColor"/>
    <!-- Radial lines -->
    <line x1="250" y1="50" x2="250" y2="100" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="250" y1="400" x2="250" y2="450" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="50" y1="250" x2="100" y2="250" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="400" y1="250" x2="450" y2="250" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"/>
    <!-- Diagonal lines -->
    <line x1="109" y1="109" x2="144" y2="144" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8"/>
    <line x1="391" y1="109" x2="356" y2="144" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8"/>
    <line x1="109" y1="391" x2="144" y2="356" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8"/>
    <line x1="391" y1="391" x2="356" y2="356" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8"/>
    <!-- Nodes -->
    <circle cx="250" cy="60" r="5" fill="currentColor"/>
    <circle cx="250" cy="440" r="5" fill="currentColor"/>
    <circle cx="60" cy="250" r="5" fill="currentColor"/>
    <circle cx="440" cy="250" r="5" fill="currentColor"/>
    <circle cx="116" cy="116" r="4" fill="currentColor"/>
    <circle cx="384" cy="116" r="4" fill="currentColor"/>
    <circle cx="116" cy="384" r="4" fill="currentColor"/>
    <circle cx="384" cy="384" r="4" fill="currentColor"/>
    <!-- Inner cross -->
    <line x1="250" y1="160" x2="250" y2="220" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5"/>
    <line x1="160" y1="250" x2="220" y2="250" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5"/>
    <line x1="280" y1="250" x2="340" y2="250" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5"/>
    <line x1="250" y1="280" x2="250" y2="340" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5"/>
  </svg>

  <div class="hero-label">Reflexión educativa — 2024</div>

  <h1 class="hero-title">
    <span>Educación</span>
    <em>&amp; Tecnología</em>
  </h1>

  <p class="hero-sub">El impacto de las herramientas digitales en el proceso de enseñanza y aprendizaje del siglo XXI.</p>

  <div class="hero-scroll">
    <div class="scroll-line"></div>
    Desplaza para explorar
  </div>

</section>

<hr class="hr-fancy">

<!-- BLOCK 1: Transformación -->
<section>
  <div class="s-tag">01 — Transformación</div>

  <div class="big-block">
    <div class="big-num">01</div>
    <div class="body-text reveal">
      En las últimas décadas, la tecnología ha <span class="highlight">transformado profundamente</span> la manera en que se desarrolla el proceso educativo. El acceso a internet, las <span class="amber">plataformas virtuales</span> y las herramientas digitales han permitido nuevas formas de enseñanza y aprendizaje, facilitando el acceso a la información y promoviendo entornos educativos <span class="mint">más interactivos</span>.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="stats-bar reveal" style="transition-delay:0.2s">
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-val" style="--sv-c: var(--electric)">∞</span>
      <span class="stat-lbl">Información disponible</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-val" style="--sv-c: var(--amber)">24/7</span>
      <span class="stat-lbl">Acceso al aprendizaje</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-val" style="--sv-c: var(--mint)">+</span>
      <span class="stat-lbl">Entornos interactivos</span>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>

<hr class="hr-fancy">

<!-- BLOCK 2: Desafíos -->
<section>
  <div class="s-tag">02 — Desafíos</div>

  <div class="body-text reveal" style="max-width: 700px; margin-bottom: 60px; font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);">
    Sin embargo, el uso de la tecnología también presenta <span class="coral">desafíos importantes</span> que no pueden ignorarse.
  </div>

  <div class="challenges-list">
    <div class="challenge-item reveal" style="--c: var(--coral)">
      <div class="ci-label">Desafío 01</div>
      <h4>Sobreinformación</h4>
      <p>La abundancia de contenido digital puede abrumar a los estudiantes, dificultando la selección de fuentes confiables y relevantes para el aprendizaje.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="challenge-item reveal" style="--c: var(--amber); transition-delay: 0.15s">
      <div class="ci-label">Desafío 02</div>
      <h4>Distracciones digitales</h4>
      <p>Las redes sociales, notificaciones y entretenimiento compiten directamente con el tiempo y la atención dedicados al proceso educativo.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="challenge-item reveal" style="--c: var(--mint); transition-delay: 0.3s">
      <div class="ci-label">Desafío 03</div>
      <h4>Calidad de la información</h4>
      <p>La falta de habilidades para evaluar críticamente la veracidad y calidad de la información disponible en línea puede afectar gravemente el aprendizaje.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>

<hr class="hr-fancy">

<!-- BLOCK 3: El Docente -->
<section>
  <div class="s-tag">03 — El rol docente</div>

  <div class="cards">
    <div class="card reveal" style="--accent: var(--electric)">
      <span class="card-num">// FUNCIÓN CENTRAL</span>
      <span class="card-icon">🎓</span>
      <h3>Guía fundamental</h3>
      <p>El papel del docente sigue siendo fundamental: no solo enseña contenidos, sino que orienta a los estudiantes en el uso responsable y crítico de las herramientas tecnológicas.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card reveal" style="--accent: var(--amber); transition-delay: 0.15s">
      <span class="card-num">// PENSAMIENTO CRÍTICO</span>
      <span class="card-icon">🔍</span>
      <h3>Evaluación crítica</h3>
      <p>Formar estudiantes capaces de analizar, cuestionar y validar la información que encuentran en entornos digitales, más allá de la mera recepción pasiva de datos.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card reveal" style="--accent: var(--mint); transition-delay: 0.3s">
      <span class="card-num">// USO RESPONSABLE</span>
      <span class="card-icon">⚡</span>
      <h3>Uso ético y consciente</h3>
      <p>Orientar hacia un uso reflexivo de la tecnología, reconociendo tanto sus potencialidades como sus riesgos en el contexto educativo contemporáneo.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>

<!-- QUOTE -->
<section class="quote-section">
  <p class="big-quote reveal">
    El docente del futuro no es quien más sabe de tecnología, sino quien mejor sabe <em style="color: var(--electric)">integrarla al aprendizaje.</em>
  </p>
</section>

<hr class="hr-fancy">

<!-- BLOCK 4: Futuro -->
<section>
  <div class="s-tag">04 — Educación del futuro</div>

  <div class="big-block">
    <div class="body-text reveal" style="font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.2vw, 1.7rem);">
      Pensar en la educación del futuro implica reconocer que la tecnología continuará <span class="highlight">evolucionando</span>. Por ello, los docentes deben prepararse para integrar estos recursos de manera <span class="amber">pedagógica</span>, promoviendo el pensamiento crítico, la <span class="coral">creatividad</span> y el aprendizaje <span class="mint">significativo</span>.
    </div>
    <div class="big-num" style="text-align: right;">04</div>
  </div>

  <div class="cards" style="margin-top: 80px;">
    <div class="card reveal" style="--accent: var(--coral)">
